The paper deals with a problem related to location-based services (LBS) and spatio-textual data, which involves indexing and searching large amounts of data efficiently. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.DB (databases), cs.IR (information retrieval), cs.SI (social and information networks), cs.DS (data structures and algorithms), and cs.CL (computation and language).
